{
  "stem": "523.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they take with a wagon, with a horse and buggy, throwing all the dead people on that wagon, out somewhere in a cemetery, throwing them to the mass grave.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never seen-- I not-- I just remember they were thrown in this wagon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But where they were buried, I never knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because it was somewhere in a field.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Jews weren't even allowed to go there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was very sick by then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother was half and half, but I was at that time very sick.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My body was full with sores.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was swollen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was crying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was dizzy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I [INAUDIBLE] didn't even know-- I think I didn't know what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was just standing-- I think we're already so destroyed morally, even children, that that-- that person didn't mean anything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because wherever we were going to looking, people are dead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People were all around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "People were dying on the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at that winter was one of the very coldest winter remembered in the history-- so much snow, if a person will die-- you could-- they fall-- just exhaustion, he fell, the snow will cover him.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he will freeze to death.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nobody will bother to pick him up to help, because each time another person died.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So me and my brother were left alone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was 10.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My brother was about 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So some people from my hometown-- they said that they are relatives, but their son left some clothes for my parents.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at that time-- it might sound funny now-- but a piece of clothing means a piece of bread-- a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he took us to-- to be with him.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
